ISLAMABAD, Mar 4 (APP): Prime Minister Imran Khan Friday here held a meeting with Governor Sindh Imran Ismail and Minister for Planning Asad Umar and exchanged views on the ongoing development projects of the federal government in Sindh and the overall political situation in the province.
The Prime Minister directed that the development projects especially those of public welfare should be completed in the stipulated time.
